aries]]'' || The New Man || Episode: \"The Game\"\n|-\n| 1996\u20132000 || ''[[The Pretender (TV series)|The Pretender]]'' || Jarod || 86 episodes<br>Nominated\u2014[[Satellite Award for Best Actor \u2013 Television Series Drama]] <small>(1998\u201399)</small><br>Nominated\u2014[[Saturn Award for Best Actor on Television]]\n|-\n| 1999-2000 || ''[[Profiler (TV series)|Profiler]]'' || Jarod || 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2000 || ''[[Men in Black: The Series]]'' || {{n/a}} || Episode: \"The Baby Kay Syndrome\"\n|-\n| 2001 || ''[[The Zeta Project]]'' || Dr. Winhelm || Episode: \"Absolute Zero\"\n|-\n| 2001\u20132003 || ''[[The Legend of Tarzan (TV series)|The Legend of Tarzan]]'' || Tarzan || 39 episodes\n|-\n| 2002 || ''[[Jackie Chan Adventures]]'' || Giles || Episode: \"Pleasure Calls\"\n|-\n| 2002\u20132005 || ''[[Justice League (TV series)|Justice League]]'' || Etrigan the Demon/Jason Blood || 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2003 || ''[[The Mummy (TV series)|The Mummy]]'' || Nizam Toth || 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2003\u20132004 || ''[[Crossing Jordan]]'' || James Horton || 4 episodes\n|-\n| 2005 || ''[[Clubhouse (TV series)|Clubhouse]]'' || Jackie Tambler || Episode: \"Save Situation\"\n|-\n| 2005\u20132007 || ''[[Higglytown Heroes]]'' || Mountain Rescue Hero || 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2009\u20132011 || ''[[Batman: The Brave and the Bold]]'' || [[Adam Strange]] || 2 episodes\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Blue Bloods (TV series)|Blue Bloods]]'' || Sonny Malevsky || 4 episodes\n|-\n| 2011 || ''[[Burn Notice (TV series)|Burn Notice]]'' || Holcomb || Episode: \"Army of One\"\n|-\n| 2012\u20132013 || ''[[Young Justice (TV series)|Young Justice]]'' || [[Captain Atom]] || 7 episodes\n|-\n|}\n\n===Theatre===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Title !! Role !! Notes\n|-\n| 2007 || ''Scarcity'' || Herb || Nominated\u2014[[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Featured Actor in a Play]]\n|-\n\n| 2009 || ''[[Impressionism (play)|Impressionism]]'' || Douglas Finch || \n|-\n| 2010 || ''[[The Elaborate Entrance of Chad 